Log Template Extraction

The automatic log template extraction feature implements the Drain algorithm
as described in the following academic paper:

  "Drain: An Online Log Parsing Approach with Fixed Depth Tree"
  Pinjia He, Jieming Zhu, Zibin Zheng, and Michael R. Lyu
  IEEE International Conference on Web Services (ICWS), 2017
  https://jiemingzhu.github.io/pub/pjhe_icws2017.pdf

This is an independent implementation based on the published algorithm.
For reference, the logpai/Drain3 implementation is available under MIT License:
  https://github.com/logpai/Drain3

